Package io.anserini.collection

Class ClueWeb12Collection.Document

java.lang.Object
io.anserini.collection.ClueWeb09Collection.Document
io.anserini.collection.ClueWeb12Collection.Document
All Implemented Interfaces:
SourceDocument
Enclosing class:
ClueWeb12Collection
public static class ClueWeb12Collection.Document
extends ClueWeb09Collection.Document
A document from the ClueWeb12 collection. This class derives from tools provided by CMU for reading the ClueWeb12 collection. Note that the implementation inherits from ClueWeb09Collection.Document for historic reasons, since the code originally developed for reading ClueWeb09 was subsequently adapted for reading ClueWeb12.
